<h1>Citrus' first trip</h1>
<p>Desperate times — desperate measures. After several months of this pandemic, several months of anxiously waiting for borders to open, several months spent at home, we decided to buy a car. We chose this little guy. It's our Citrus — citroen c4.</p>
