<p>His first trip wasn't far away, but it doesn't matter. The destination doesn't matter. What matters is the journey. And it was awesome!</p> 
<p>We've traveled to the Lotoshino town in Moscow district. Unexpectedly, it's a nice small town, very charming with animal garden in the middle.</p>
